imdb.plot outline: The unlikely story of three American political advisers - George Gorton (Donovan Darkone), Joseph Shumate (Dean Dawson), and Richard Dresner (Jeffery Mellman), who are hired to create a positive spin on Boris Yeltsin's reckless yet ultimately successful Russian presidential reelection bid mired by drunkenness and scandal.
imdb.title: Spin Doctors
